column9:
1. Why bind a mobile phone number?
 When you bind your mobile phone number- you can receive a verification code when the account settings are changed- which can timely remind you of abnormal operations that are not operated by yourself; And you can quickly set up your account or use other functions through the verification code- omitting the tedious steps of entering a password;

2.Why bind multiple account login channels?
 After binding your account- you can log in to the same BIGO LIVE account at any time and place with any bound account. And you can display your social accounts in your profile to make more friends;

1. After opening- auto renewal will be operated in each natural month and extend the VIP service for a month;
2. If you wish to cancel renewal- please close it within at least 48 hours during the withholding period;
3. How to cancel: click [Cancel auto renewal] at the top.

1. After the opening- every natural month will automatically renew and extend the VIP for 1 month;

2. If you wish to cancel the renewal- please turn off the automatic renewal at least 48 hours before the chargeback period;

3. Your VIP completes the subscription on the Android system- you need to use the Android device to cancel the renewal;

4. How to cancel: Open the Google Play store on your Android phone or tablet. Click [Menu] → [Subscribe]- select BIGO LIVE monthly subscription VIP subscription service- and click [Cancel Subscription].

1. After the opening- every natural month will automatically renew and extend the VIP for 1 month;

2. If you wish to cancel the renewal- please turn off the automatic renewal at least 48 hours before the chargeback period;

3. Your VIP completes the subscription on the iOS system- you need to use the iOS device to cancel the renewal;

4. How to cancel: From the Home page- go to [Settings] → click [iTunes Store and App store] → click [Apple ID]- select [View Apple ID] → [Account Settings] → [Subscription]- choose to cancel BIGO LIVE consecutive monthly subscription VIP can subscribe.

1. After opening- auto renewal will be operated in each natural month and extend the VIP service for a month;
2. If you wish to cancel renewal- please close it within at least 48 hours during the withholding period;
3. How to cancel: auto renewal in diamond can be cancelled on the VIP introduction page.
